metadata.name: The Call Of The Void #1
metadata.description:
The Call Of The Void #1

The first piece in a series about the void, a series about dark thoughts, how to interpret them through creating them on the physical place, made to output them rather than internalise them.

The first piece about the void series is expressed on paper with black ink. I was intimating the spiral-like calling of darkness.

"The Call Of The Void"

The first piece in "The Face, The Void" Collection.

4961px × 3508px

This is an original piece of art, created and expressed by artist Harry G.B. Crabtree, using black ink on cold-pressed paper.
© 2021 Harry George Barker Crabtree
